1. Developer Pushes Code (main branch)
   ↓
2. AWS CodePipeline Triggers
   ├─ Source Stage:
   │   └── Fetch from GitHub/GitLab/CodeCommit
   ├─ Build Stage:
   │   ├── Compile Go App (Go build/test)
   │   ├── Run Unit Tests
   │   ├── Security Scans (Snyk, Trivy, etc.)
   │   └── Create Docker Image → Push to Amazon ECR
   ├─ Staging Deploy:
   │   └── Deploy using ECS Fargate / EKS / EC2 via CDK
   │       └── Smoke Tests & Integration Tests
   ├─ Approval Stage:
   │   └── Manual Approval (QA/Lead)
   └─ Production Deploy:
       ├── Provision infra via CDK (if needed)
       └── Deploy image from ECR
